{"tid":880551,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"怕麻煩既人同我入一入黎","createTime":"2018-10-28T18:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T19:27:26.000Z","uid":209340,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc00f36cb54395059c2234ea193fb71e8e7d910","tid":880551,"uid":209340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:57:05.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得洗頭啲泡泡醃到眼覺得好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我細個嗰時成日洗頭醃到眼<br />\n自此之後每次沖涼都會帶住副泳鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到今時今日每次沖涼都會帶住副泳鏡黎沖<br />\n咁就唔怕啲啲泡泡醃到眼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a182881be1f611291139bd38b588c34416109e","tid":880551,"uid":139545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"咁同伴侶沖涼既話都會帶住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係怕水入眼<br />\n一入就唔理咁多 令條毛巾抹一抺。"},{"pid":"d171d794189bf74458f7a50abad735bdcd739447","tid":880551,"uid":209340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45a182881be1f611291139bd38b588c34416109e","tid":880551,"uid":139545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"咁同伴侶沖涼既話都會帶住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係怕水入眼<br />\n一入就唔理咁多 令條毛巾抹一抺。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T19:12:18.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊沖會問佢帶唔帶，但佢話on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後返我自己一個帶住黎沖"},{"pid":"ecfb241426d4307b5cab4594c77ca06efa380eca","tid":880551,"uid":139545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T19:15:23.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇笑你？"},{"pid":"afc508c88c81328ae62d0d29cbde23b066c25428","tid":880551,"uid":209340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecfb241426d4307b5cab4594c77ca06efa380eca","tid":880551,"uid":139545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T19:15:23.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇笑你？"},"